---
import Base from '../../layouts/Base.astro';
---
<Base title="Social Proof for Notary Publics — Collect & Display Client Testimonials | SocialProof.dev">
  <main class="for-page">
    <section class="hero">
      <div class="container">
        <div class="badge">For Notary Publics</div>
        <h1>Stand out in a sea of notaries. Let your reputation speak first.</h1>
        <p class="subtitle">When someone searches "notary near me," they often find a dozen options. The one they call is usually the one with the most credible reviews. SocialProof puts your best testimonials front and center.</p>
        <a href="https://app.socialproof.dev/register" class="btn-primary">Start free — no credit card</a>
        <p class="micro">Free forever for 1 active widget</p>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="problem">
      <div class="container">
        <h2>Notary work is transactional — trust is what makes you the one they refer</h2>
        <p>A notarization takes minutes. The client experience — your responsiveness, professionalism, accuracy — is what they remember and recommend. But that reputation mostly lives in people's heads and private text messages to friends.</p>
        <p>A testimonials section on your website (or your booking page) changes that. It gives prospects a reason to choose you over the faceless notary two blocks away — and it works 24/7 while you're doing signings.</p>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="benefits">
      <div class="container">
        <h2>Simple social proof for a straightforward service</h2>
        <div class="benefits-grid">
          <div class="benefit">
            <h3>📲 Text your link after every signing</h3>
            <p>Reach out the same day: "Thanks for booking! If you have a moment, I'd love your feedback: [link]." It takes 45 seconds to fill out and you'll be amazed how many respond.</p>
          </div>
          <div class="benefit">
            <h3>✅ Approve before publishing</h3>
            <p>All submissions come through your dashboard. You publish only what you choose. Full control.</p>
          </div>
          <div class="benefit">
            <h3>🌐 Works on any platform</h3>
            <p>Add a widget to your Notarize.com profile, website, or Calendly booking page — wherever clients evaluate you.</p>
          </div>
          <div class="benefit">
            <h3>📍 Especially powerful for mobile notaries</h3>
            <p>You go to clients. Your professionalism and reliability are your differentiators. Testimonials that capture that close more bookings.</p>
          </div>
          <div class="benefit">
            <h3>⭐ Star ratings + text</h3>
            <p>Combine ratings with written reviews to build a convincing trust package on your website — without depending on third-party platforms.</p>
          </div>
          <div class="benefit">
            <h3>🔄 Reusable link, unlimited submissions</h3>
            <p>One collection link works for every client, forever. No setup per client, no extra cost per submission on the free plan.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="sample-widget">
      <div class="container">
        <h2>What clients say about notaries who use social proof</h2>
        <div class="widget-preview">
          <blockquote>
            <p>"David came to my office at 7pm on a Friday for a last-minute document signing. Professional, accurate, and completely calm about the tight timeline. I've already referred him to three colleagues."</p>
            <footer>— Mark B., Houston TX · ⭐⭐⭐⭐⭐</footer>
          </blockquote>
        </div>
        <p>That's the kind of review that books your next client before you've even hung up the phone.</p>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="how-it-works">
      <div class="container">
        <h2>Set it up in 10 minutes, run on autopilot</h2>
        <ol class="steps">
          <li><strong>Create your free account</strong> at app.socialproof.dev</li>
          <li><strong>Copy your collection link</strong></li>
          <li><strong>Text or email it after every signing</strong> — takes 10 seconds</li>
          <li><strong>Approve testimonials</strong> in your dashboard</li>
          <li><strong>Paste the widget</strong> on your website or booking page</li>
        </ol>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="faq">
      <div class="container">
        <h2>Common questions</h2>
        <div class="faq-list">
          <div class="faq-item">
            <h3>Do clients need an account to leave a testimonial?</h3>
            <p>No. They open your link and fill out a form — name, feedback, optional rating. No login, no account creation. Just a 45-second form.</p>
          </div>
          <div class="faq-item">
            <h3>I only have a Calendly booking page, not a website. Can I still use this?</h3>
            <p>Yes. Add the widget to any HTML page — including embedding it in a simple one-page site you can create for free. Or use the collection link to gather testimonials and embed the widget when you're ready to build a site.</p>
          </div>
          <div class="faq-item">
            <h3>What's the difference between this and Google reviews?</h3>
            <p>Google reviews appear on Google Search and Maps. SocialProof puts testimonials on YOUR website where you control the presentation and placement. Both are valuable — SocialProof complements, not replaces, your Google profile.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="cta">
      <div class="container">
        <h2>Start building your testimonial collection today</h2>
        <p>Free forever for 1 active widget. No credit card. Set up in minutes.</p>
        <a href="https://app.socialproof.dev/register" class="btn-primary">Start free today</a>
        <p class="micro">Free forever for 1 active widget · No credit card required</p>
      </div>
    </section>
  </main>
</Base>
